@node about "About"

    This is my first shared library, i put here some stuff that im using a lot,
to keep my programs small as possible. So, if some program will call for this
just put this into your libs: drawer ;-)

@endnode

@node legal "Legal"

    I can't be blamed for everything that my occur due lack of your knowledge
about amiga! This pice of software is free so if you don't like it -- don't use
it.

